Dependencies
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Demeter-CSP depends on the Simple DirectMedia Layer (SDL) version >= 1.2.5.
SDL can be obtained from http://www.libsdl.org/


Compiling Demeter-CSP:
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Demeter-CSP is part of the complete CSP build.  Refer to the README instructions
in the top-level CSP directory for more information.


